      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nThe following sessions will be run for build 100871 patch 2\n\nEnforced:\n- review-ldiskfs-dne on el8.8-x86_64/ldiskfs servers and clients\n- review-ldiskfs-dne-arm on el8.8-x86_64/ldiskfs servers and el8.8-aarch64/ldiskfs clients\n\nMaloo Test Queue: https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_queue?jobs=lustre-reviews&builds=100871&commit=Apply+Filter\nMaloo Results: https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/related?jobs=lustre-reviews&builds=100871#redirect",
