        "subject": "LU-9619 contrib: rewrite prepare-commit-msg in python",
        "message": "LU-9619 contrib: rewrite prepare-commit-msg in python\n\nThis would make it much easier to implement advanced\nfunctionality, such as automatically detecting the\ncorrect Test-Parameters for a patch.\n\nThe only dependency to run this hook is python3.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Timothy Day <timday@amazon.com>\nChange-Id: Iefe5dd9ffc30e8c789bb3e0d034fc848d9007d7a\n"
